        "action": "Sufferers of fibromyalgia & Behcet's Disease to automatically qualify for PIP",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "My wife suffers from fibromyalgia and Behcet's disease.  Both are long term debilitating illnesses which impact massively on her day to day life.  She is in constant pain, and is unable to cope with day-to-day activities.  The DWP withdrew her PIP, based on an uninformed and inadequate assessment.",
